#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn14.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn14.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 14 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 14 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Catutthavagga "
msgstr "4. The Fourth Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn14.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Samaṇabrāhmaṇasutta "
msgstr "37. Ascetics and Brahmins "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.176, sc1
msgctxt "sn14.37:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.37:1.2"
msgid "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, dhātuyo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four elements. "

msgctxt "sn14.37:1.3"
msgid "Katamā catasso? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn14.37:1.4"
msgid "Pathavīdhātu, āpodhātu, tejodhātu, vāyodhātu. "
msgstr "The elements of earth, water, fire, and air. "

msgctxt "sn14.37:1.5"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imāsaṃ catunnaṃ dhātūnaṃ assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who don’t truly understand these four elements’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are. "

msgctxt "sn14.37:1.6"
msgid "na me te, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu vā samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu vā brāhmaṇasammatā; na ca pana te āyasmanto sāmaññatthaṃ vā brahmaññatthaṃ vā diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharanti. "
msgstr "I don’t regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables don’t realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and don’t live having realized it with their own insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn14.37:2.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imāsaṃ catunnaṃ dhātūnaṃ assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who do truly understand these four elements’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are. "

msgctxt "sn14.37:2.2"
msgid "te ca kho me, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu ceva samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu ca brāhmaṇasammatā; te ca panāyasmanto sāmaññatthañca brahmaññatthañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti. "
msgstr "I regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and live having realized it with their own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn14.37:2.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
